  "id": "RAW_ce60b696",
  "title": "AI 是繁荣还是泡沫？哈佛学者剖析 OpenAI 千亿交易背后的风险",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247619363&idx=2&sn=9a447e937a76246380eb35ab1bcb6edc",
  "date": "2025-10-18 01:58:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"334\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100135677\" data-ratio=\"0.5946666666666667\" width=\"840\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"499\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;display:block;letter-spacing:inherit;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2284ad2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBL6qslPWDByv1Sf6YDtIguUVZQ7RFxNmHGGayZicMoFZAedQic6Y1hUo7zRPiasHsgicicRibFlJChQS4Sw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当OpenAI与Nvidia、AMD接连达成数百亿美元的合作协议时，投资者们欢呼雀跃。但一些敏锐的观察者却看到了令人不安的熟悉景象——这与上世纪90年代互联网泡沫时期的\"循环融资\"如出一辙。《哈佛商业评论》最新文章发出警告：这场万亿美元的AI狂欢，可能正在重演历史。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><i><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: normal;\">以下为文章编译，原文：《Is AI a Boom or a Bubble?》</span></span></i></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Nvidia对OpenAI的1000亿美元承诺，以及OpenAI对芯片的对等采购，标志着一场正在全速推进的AI军备竞赛。领导者如何理解这个市场？对近期历史的审视，特别是当下与互联网泡沫之间的相似之处，提供了一些线索。投机资本和循环融资可能扭曲时机和预期，尤其是在AI应用仍然不均衡的情况下。目前，消费者的热情超过了企业的整合速度，这增加了产能过剩的风险。持久的优势将来自纪律性投资、将AI嵌入工作流程，以及塑造平衡创新与韧性的治理框架。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">循环融资的阴影</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年9月下旬，Nvidia宣布计划向OpenAI投资高达1000亿美元，用于资助新一代数据中心的建设，而OpenAI则承诺为这些设施采购数百万片Nvidia芯片。几天后，OpenAI又与AMD达成了类似的数十亿美元协议。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些交易受到投资者的热烈欢迎，但也引发了质疑。在一些观察者看来，这些交易与1990年代末期的循环融资安排有着诡异的相似之处——当时，供应商和客户相互抬高彼此的估值，却并未创造真正的价值。彭博社对这一模式的描述恰如其分：这是一个\"日益复杂且相互关联的商业交易网络\"，正在推动一场万亿美元规模的AI繁荣。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI的快速建设正在重塑高管决策并压缩时间表。对AI没有清晰的观点不再是一个选项。资本流动迅速，基础设施正以前所未有的规模被投入，竞争压力在加剧。在这个新环境中，速度和意图很重要，那些将资源投入到回报持久的领域、识别出值得拥抱的趋势、避免无法持续的押注的公司，将会蓬勃发展。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">创新与投机的交汇</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当今领导者面临的核心挑战是如何平衡AI的长期前景与短期回报的压力。AI经济受到两场竞赛的推动：一场是争夺霸权的地缘政治竞赛，另一场是产生必要回报以证明惊人投资规模的金融竞赛。当这两股力量汇聚时，它们相互放大，加剧了过度投资的风险。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">与早期泡沫的相似之处令人震惊。在互联网泡沫时期，资本涌入电信基础设施，押注指数级的互联网需求。当需求滞后时，破产潮席卷整个行业。问题不在于互联网缺乏潜力，而在于资本部署的时机超前于应用普及。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，我们看到了类似的信号。市场集中度达到了惊人水平：\"七巨头\"科技公司占标普500指数的三分之一以上，这一比例是2000年泡沫时期顶级科技公司的两倍。AI公司的估值基于激进的预测而非当前收益。复杂的交易结构，如OpenAI通过供应商协议进行的融资，类似于过去泡沫的循环性。与此同时，大量资金正被投入数据中心、芯片供应链和基础模型，而企业采用速度远比消费者热情更为谨慎。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100135678\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" width=\"6958\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"3900\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d27f745&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBL6qslPWDByv1Sf6YDtIguUhjdPXD09V11bzQZpw7Bl7PhFiaokxUxZFWw2icMo0jquCvlSuNScDkdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">消费者热情与企业谨慎</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">应用出现了分化。消费者以创纪录的速度拥抱ChatGPT，其达到1亿用户的速度超过了此前任何应用。但企业仍然犹豫不决。麻省理工学院发现大规模生产力提升难以实现，并建议专注于高价值用途、将AI嵌入工作流程并逐步扩展。根据斯坦福大学的AI指数，企业采用率从2023年的55%上升到2024年的78%。然而，企业仍然保持谨慎，将隐私、可靠性、合规性、安全性和财务风险列为主要障碍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">围绕消费者使用的炒作尚未转化为广泛的企业变革。基础设施建设假设应用将会跟进，但企业很少在看不到财务回报前景的情况下做出承诺。如果需求滞后，当今大规模的芯片和数据中心建设可能造成产能过剩。这一动态进一步被产业政策和国家安全优先事项所加剧，这些政策将投资置于消费之前，虽然促进了增长，但也放大了泡沫风险。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">产业政策、资本流动与AI地缘政治</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">美国政府之手曾塑造美国的技术周期，通常通过创造激励、进行针对性投资，然后让产业自行扩展。在1990年代，华盛顿通过私有化网络基础设施、通过1996年电信法开放市场、制定第230条限制平台责任，推动了互联网的扩张。这些选择创造了增长、投资和创新的条件。今天，政策制定者正在将类似的策略应用于人工智能。特朗普和拜登政府都强调产业政策，将AI不仅框定为经济机遇，也是国家安全当务之急。对企业的隐含信息是：速度比谨慎更重要。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">欧洲专注于风险管理，但对过度监管的担忧促使CEO们警告竞争力丧失。作为回应，布鲁塞尔启动了\"AI大陆行动计划\"和10亿欧元的\"应用AI\"倡议，以加速采用、降低合规成本，并将欧洲打造成全球AI领导者。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，AI初创公司的风险投资超过了此前加密货币和移动技术的周期，主权财富基金增添了另一波投资。这些参与者在应用普及之前就刻意投资，押注需求最终会实现。如果没有实现，供应过剩可能会留下搁浅资产，就像互联网泡沫破裂后未使用的电信光纤一样。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，企业面临着不同的决策。对它们而言，挑战不是是否为下一波基础设施浪潮提供资金，而是如何以加强自身业务的方式采用AI。那些在互联网泡沫中幸存下来的公司，如亚马逊，专注于为电子商务构建基础设施，它们通过将技术投资与业务联系起来而非投机动能获得成功。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">理解约束条件</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">资本和政策正在加速AI竞赛，但约束限制了其速度。土地、劳动力和能源为采用规模的扩展速度设置了硬性界限。这些限制造成了稀缺性：早期行动者获得能力和优势，而落后者则掉队。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了理解这些约束如何影响AI的轨迹，有必要重新审视AI三要素的概念：算力、数据和人才。这些元素定义了过去十年的AI发展。现在出现了新的三要素：土地、劳动力和能源。数据中心需要拥有电力和水资源的大型场地，而社区正在抵制其足迹。劳动力短缺不仅限于工程师，还延伸到电工、建筑工人和技术人员等技术工种。能源是最严峻的约束：高盛预测到2030年美国数据中心的能源消耗将翻倍，威胁到在没有可持续解决方案的情况下扩展的经济性。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100135679\" data-ratio=\"0.7506666666666667\" width=\"2048\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"1536\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a166fb95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBL6qslPWDByv1Sf6YDtIguU9ntDHTNrDSLFQlHlaSd9vlOqcRYfPRk3Yqf2cfBw0QtwzpDc2JbEHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI可能是一项通用技术，但其基础设施并非无限可扩展。对公司而言，这意味着将新的三要素直接纳入战略。获得长期能源合同、与技术学校建立劳动力合作伙伴关系、与当地社区就土地使用进行合作，都可以减少瓶颈风险。那些预见这些压力并提前锁定能力的公司，将比那些假设无限可扩展性的公司更有能力获得持久回报。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是泡沫吗？</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以肯定的是，并非所有人都认为这是泡沫。Nvidia首席执行官黄仁勋认为AI需求是结构性的而非投机性的，将今天的建设比作\"新工业革命的开端\"。</span></p>\n  <figure style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100135680\" data-ratio=\"0.5626666666666666\" width=\"1200\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"675\" style=\"border: 0px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;width: 629px;display: block;letter-spacing: inherit;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2641142&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBL6qslPWDByv1Sf6YDtIguUT8eSymwuFJcWXEePyjxL0WCYG5rAQXPvlSWzFLpbCUOMKka0u6mHwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在与Stratechery的Ben Thompson的访谈中，Sam Altman驳斥了对当今AI投资不可持续的担忧，将OpenAI的战略框定为超越聊天机器人，转向代理型AI和连接基础设施与应用的平台。\"要有足够的基础设施来满足需求是极其困难的，\"他指出，强调了前置资本与延迟回报之间的紧张关系。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在他2024年的著作《共同智能：与AI共同生活和工作》中，Ethan Mollick讨论了AI如何在工作场所和教室中产生实际的、渐进的改进。通过增强人类能力，产生小的、累积的收益，AI逐渐建立起更广泛的影响。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">观点的分歧反映了核心的不确定性，因为泡沫的关键不在于技术的长期影响，而在于应用和资本周期是否一致。互联网是革命性的，但这并没有阻止互联网泡沫的崩溃。AI很可能重塑全球产业，但其财务基础仍可能动摇。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">领导者如何捕捉价值</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于商业领导者而言，成功需要专注和严谨。将AI作为快速解决方案是错误的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的变革需要建立准备适应AI的文化、在高价值领域进行有针对性的押注、并将AI嵌入运营。那些经受住互联网泡沫崩溃的公司，如eBay和Netflix，通过敏锐的战略专注和快速的运营适应做到了这一点。它们抵制了炒作驱动的分心。今天，沃尔玛使用AI库存机器人将过剩库存削减35%并将准确性提高15%，在降低成本的同时改善库存率和客户体验。它还刚刚与OpenAI签订协议，允许用户直接通过ChatGPT购买其产品。赢家将在强化其核心优势的地方嵌入AI，而不是追逐每一个新趋势。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">领导者应该将资源投入数据治理，并重新设计组织以便人与AI能够有效协作。人员准备涉及持续的技能再培训和角色演变。耐心至关重要，因为企业转型是一个多年旅程，价值随时间捕获，而不是追求投机收益。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果高管只将AI视为支出竞赛，他们就错过了重点。挑战在于设计推动创新并保护社会的治理。正如我在《治理的十字路口》中所论述的，当AI政策随技术演进时效果最好，在推动创新的同时不失去安全性和公平性。监管沙盒为实验提供受控环境同时保持问责制，公私合作伙伴关系可以嵌入透明度和风险管理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">那些及早参与的公司将对AI经济如何治理产生影响，帮助确保应用与韧性、公平监督和对技术的持久信任相匹配。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">既深远又脆弱</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">人工智能既深远又脆弱。其长期轨迹指向重新定义产业、重塑工作和改变全球权力平衡。在短期内，地缘政治竞争与放松监管政策和投机资本相结合，创造了与过去泡沫极为相似的条件。历史的教训不是泡沫使技术变得毫无价值，而是它们扭曲了时机和预期。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">忽视AI就是冒着过时的风险。成功将来自纪律性采用和务实的公司治理。那些专注于将AI嵌入工作流程并培养能够适应的劳动力的领导者将获得持久价值。那些及早参与新兴治理框架的人将帮助塑造AI经济的规则。这一时刻将被铭记为AI驱动经济的开端，还是过度扩张，取决于高管和投资者今天做出的决策。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 8px 24px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;hyphens:auto;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgvluv80xol\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgvluv891r74\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">整理：周华香</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "哈佛学者警示当前 AI 产业存在“循环融资”和“产能过剩”风险，与互联网泡沫有惊人相似之处，并提出应对策略。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "哈佛学者警示当前 AI 产业存在“循环融资”和“产能过剩”风险，与互联网泡沫有惊人相似之处，并提出应对策略。",
  "summary": "文章深入剖析了当前 AI 产业繁荣背后可能隐藏的风险，核心观点是 AI 领域正出现与上世纪 90 年代末互联网泡沫时期类似的“循环融资”现象。文章指出，Nvidia 和 OpenAI 之间高达千亿美元的合作协议，以及 OpenAI 与 AMD 的类似交易，可能构成供应商与客户相互抬高估值的循环融资模式。地缘政治竞争与金融回报压力相互放大，加剧了 AI 领域的过度投资风险。同时，文章强调消费者对 AI 的热情远超企业实际采用速度，这可能导致芯片和数据中心等基础设施的产能过剩。此外，文章还提出了 AI 发展面临的土地、劳动力和能源“新三要素”物理约束。为避免重蹈历史覆辙，文章建议企业领导者应专注于 AI 的纪律性采用、将其嵌入工作流程、进行有针对性的投资，并积极参与塑造平衡创新与韧性的治理框架，而非盲目追逐投机性炒作。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 产业的“循环融资”模式与互联网泡沫时期相似，可能扭曲市场估值。",
      "explanation": "供应商与客户之间的大额互投，可能导致估值虚高，缺乏真实价值创造，重演历史上的投机性泡沫。"
    },
    {
      "point": "消费者热情与企业谨慎之间的鸿沟，可能引发 AI 基础设施的产能过剩。",
      "explanation": "大规模的芯片和数据中心建设基于对未来需求的激进预测，若企业采用滞后，可能造成资源浪费。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 发展受土地、劳动力和能源等“新三要素”的物理约束。",
      "explanation": "数据中心对场地、电力和水资源需求巨大，技术劳动力短缺，能源消耗翻倍，这些限制了 AI 的无限扩展性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "领导者应通过纪律性投资和务实治理，将 AI 嵌入业务流程以捕捉持久价值。",
      "explanation": "避免盲目追逐炒作，聚焦高价值应用，强化核心优势，同时参与构建平衡创新与韧性的治理框架。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "《哈佛商业评论》最新文章发出警告：这场万亿美元的 AI 狂欢，可能正在重演历史。",
    "在一些观察者看来，这些交易与 1990 年代末期的循环融资安排有着诡异的相似之处——当时，供应商和客户相互抬高彼此的估值，却并未创造真正的价值。",
    "问题不在于互联网缺乏潜力，而在于资本部署的时机超前于应用普及。",
    "如果需求滞后，当今大规模的芯片和数据中心建设可能造成产能过剩。",
    "能源是最严峻的约束：高盛预测到 2030 年美国数据中心的能源消耗将翻倍，威胁到在没有可持续解决方案的情况下扩展的经济性。"
  ],
